manifest.description: This folder shows the structure of the Submission file.
This geo file contains the different geometries for the train set.
This geo file contains the different geometries for the test set.

This sample file shows the paths to the raster images for train set. These path names should be changed to reflect the directory of your data. It only shows the data downloaded for the month of January, so it is not a full set.
